; Coverage for report.cc fn_nail_down with balance type
; When --historical is used with multiple commodities in one account,
; the total is a balance which triggers the BALANCE case

P 2024/01/01 AAPL $150.00
P 2024/01/01 GOOG $100.00

2024/01/01 Buy stocks
    Assets:Stocks    10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Stocks    5 GOOG @ $100.00
    Assets:Cash     $-2000.00

test bal --historical Assets:Stocks
            $2000.00  Assets:Stocks
end test
